bill_title: H.R.3383 - 119th Congress (2025-2026): Incentivizing New Ventures and Economic Strength Through Capital Formation Act of 2025 | Congress.gov | Library of Congress
brief_summary: Shown Here: Reported to House (06/25/2025) Increasing Investor Opportunities Act This bill allows a closed-end fund—a portfolio of pooled assets with a limited number of shares traded on an exchange—to increase its investment in private investment funds.
